namaH svaahaa, yamaayedaM na mama&lt;/FONT=\r\n&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;OM =\r\nprajaapateye namaH svaahaa, prajaapateya idaM na mama&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV ali=\r\ngn=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;OM raahave namaH sv=\r\naahaa, raahava idaM na mama (Rahu =3D spirit of breaking barriers)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/=\r\nDIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;OM gom=\r\naatre namaH svaahaa, gomaatra idaM na mama&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;=\r\nFONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;OM sarpebhyo namaH svaahaa, sa=\r\nrpebhya idaM na mama&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 s=\r\nize=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;OM ketave namaH svaahaa, ketava idaM na mama (Ketu =\r\n=3D detachment)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=\r\n=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;OM chitraguptaaya namaH svaahaa, chitraguptaayedaM na m=\r\nama&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVe=\r\nrdana&gt;OM brahmaNe namaH svaahaa, brahmaNa idaM na mama&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV al=\r\nign=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV=\r\n&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp;&nb=\r\nsp; Dasa Dikpalakas (rulers of ten direction we take in life, in terms of o=\r\nur work):&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 fac=\r\ne=3DVerdana&gt;OM indraaya namaH svaahaa, indraayedaM na mama (Indra =3D Power=\r\n and influence over others)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#0=\r\n00000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;OM agnaye namaH svaahaa, agnaya idaM na mama =\r\n(Agni =3D Transformation of world)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt